cs.CV, cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.NE, cs.SI 

This paper deals with medical image fusion, which is a common application of computer vision (CV). Therefore, cs.CV is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves feature selection, which is a common topic in information theory (IT) and machine learning (NE). The use of DTCWT for image decomposition and fusion is a signal processing (SI) technique. Finally, the paper deals with multimodal image fusion, which is a topic in multimedia (MM) processing.
